               <msContents>
                  <summary>
                     <p>Production unit I</p>
                     <p>I) ዜና᎓ሕማማቲሁ᎓ለመድኃኔ᎓ዓለም“Story of the Sufferings of the Savior of the World”, revealed to Mary Magdalen, Birgit (Barzeda) and Elizabeth (fols. <locus from="2ra" to="5va"/>), a version of the apocryphal “Story of the Passions of Christ”, see Piovanelli <locus target="#2014 #2015"/>
                     </p>
                     <p>II) የኢትዮያ፡ ታሪክ “A History of Ethiopia” (fols. <locus from="5v" to="12v"/>), in Gǝˁǝz and Amharic, starting with the genealogy of Adam and ending with the battle of Sägäle (<locus target="#27"/>October <locus target="#1916"/>)</p>
                     <p>Production unit II</p>
                     <p>III) ጸሎተ፡ ኪዳን፡ ዘሠለስቱ፡ ጊዜያት“Covenant Prayer of the Three Times” (fols. <locus from="16r" to="24r"/>) </p>
                     <p>IV) መሰተብቍዓት, ዘይነግሥ፡ ዘቅዱስ፡ ያሬድ, Supplications (fols. <locus from="24r" to="55r"/>)</p>
                     <p>V) ሥርዓተ፡ ቡራኬ“Order of Blessing” (fols. <locus from="55v" to="58r"/>), different from Yä-burakeyat śǝrˁat printed in some Ethiopian editions of the Missal; but cp. MS EMML no. <locus target="#1206"/>(Getatchew Haile <locus target="#1979"/>:<locus target="#173"/>)  </p>
                     <p>VI) Text of a festive liturgical service which accompanies the Anaphoras (fols. <locus from="59r" to="80v"/>).</p>
